<subSubSection id="C3216524FFDBFFA6FF43F939FDF9F887" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8436AFFFDBFFA6FF43F939FDF9F887" blockId="2.[136,1452,1703,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">
In the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FEA4F939FDC8F933" authorityName="Turczaninow" authorityYear="1858" box="[367,515,1704,1730]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ferruginea">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FEA4F939FDC8F933" box="[367,515,1704,1730]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. ferruginea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the specimen n.378 collected by 
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FC4AF936FC70F930" box="[897,955,1703,1729]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Funk</emphasis>
is quoted without specifying the herbarium, but the author worked at and left much of his collection in KW (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FCF7F95AFBF0F914" author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[828,1083,1739,1766]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 537–538), with duplicates in other herbaria. Two specimens were found in KW and P, and we designated herein specimen KW001000107 as the 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFDBFFA6FF43F882FF24F8DC" box="[136,239,1811,1837]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FEDFF885FE6CF8DF" authorityName="Turczaninow" authorityYear="1858" box="[276,423,1812,1838]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ferruginea">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FEDFF885FE6CF8DF" box="[276,423,1812,1838]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. ferruginea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in accordance with Art. 9.3 of the ICN, by choosing the best-preserved specimen. Based on the type materials, the application of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FD5DF8A9FCE2F8A3" authorityName="Turczaninow" authorityYear="1858" box="[662,809,1848,1874]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ferruginea">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FD5DF8A9FCE2F8A3" box="[662,809,1848,1874]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. ferruginea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confirmed as a heterotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FAC3F8A9FA4EF8A0" authorityName="Willdenow" authorityYear="1801" box="[1288,1413,1848,1873]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FAC3F8A9FA4EF8A0" box="[1288,1413,1848,1873]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. speciosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as previously accepted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FE5AF8CDFDE6F887" author="Burret, K. E. M." box="[401,557,1883,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="592 - 880" refId="ref7098" refString="Burret, K. E. M. (1926) Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Tiliaceen. Notizblatt des Botanischen Gartens und Museums zu Berlin-Dahlem 9 (88): 592 - 880. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3994327" type="journal article" year="1926">Burret (1926)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
